gameforge.main_quest_lv1._20_say = "The exciting adventures of Metin2 are about to[ENTER]begin. For starters, please find the City Guard.[ENTER]He will provide you with some basic information[ENTER]and various assignments.[ENTER][ENTER]If you would like to go hunting, you will find[ENTER]wild animals on the outskirts of the village[ENTER]borders. They will be shown on the minimap as red[ENTER]dots. You should concentrate on the Wild Dogs[ENTER]first, as they are the easiest targets.[ENTER]Good luck! "
