gameforge.main_quest_lv97._230_say = "Yes, I should be able to decrypt these characters[ENTER]without a problem. Although, to be able to do so,[ENTER]I require Fossil Earth. The alchemist probably[ENTER]has a clump of it lying about. Please go and ask[ENTER]him for it. "
